snippet.title: Ace Combat 7: Skies Unknown - PS4/XB1/PC - Dev Diary #1
snippet.description:
Fly behind the scenes of ACE COMBAT 7: SKIES UNKNOWN with this exclusive interview of the Ace team, featuring Brand Director Kazutoki Kono, and learn more about the making of the game.

Pilot the skies on January 18 on PS4 & XB1 and February 1 on PC: http://bnent.eu/BuyAceCombat7
